        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Jeff Lynn became a non-executive board member in March 2013.  He was re-appointed for a second term on the 29 February 2017. He is executive chairman and co-founder of Seedrs, one of the worldâ€™s leading equity crowdfunding platforms. He was also founding chairman of the Coalition for a Digital Economy (Coadec), which advocates on behalf of digital startups and small medium enterprises on policy and regulatory issues.</p>

<p>Jeff began his career as a corporate lawyer, practising with Sullivan and Cromwell LLP in New York and London.</p>
</div>
